01:06:30.602 --> 01:06:31.785
What?

01:06:31.853 --> 01:06:33.503
I already made
all the arrangements.

01:06:35.106 --> 01:06:37.374
Oh.

01:06:37.442 --> 01:06:40.010
Well, when were you thinking
of having the...

