I need faith.

01:13:07.949 --> 01:13:13.119
Faith is just believing
in something beyond yourself,

01:13:13.187 --> 01:13:18.341
something you can't feel,
or smell, or touch,

01:13:18.409 --> 01:13:21.111
like hope or love.

01:13:24.181 --> 01:13:26.549
